It seems you're having a tough time with the Guard Drone...
Can't be helped.

This is a device that forcibly stops the operation of the
Spirit Power Reflector. With this, you can avoid having your
magic attacks reflected.

drone and open the way to the first floor.
I'm looking forward to it, Amagawa Kohane-chan.

operation of the Spirit Power Reflector. With this, you can
endure magical attacks without reflecting them.
I'm counting on you, Amagawa Kohane-chan.
